channel.title: Ya I need a bit of help with private servers
channel.description:
If you flame me you will not get a reply. People who flame newbs for being NEW at something are just noobs themselves. Now I'm not incompentant, I've been searching for 2 straight days all over this site and others trying to figure out what the hell I'm supposed to do and am still stuck. So here's my problem...
I have no-ip, and hamachi, I have testscape, I'm willing to download w/e, delete w/e, but everytime I try to log onto the private server, it logs me onto someone elses :/
(BTW These errors have occered on both my hamachi and no-ip.)
So heres the thing, I've read tons of those tut's on how to make a private server, and I've got testscape up and running, got the 0.0.0.0.43594 up and running. So I try to log on with that up and running and it'll say "Error: unable to starup listener on 43594 - port already in use?" That's what it says on running bot. So here I am, just really really confused, as for the administration stuff, try to help me out on that or w/e but I've searched all over test scape and hybridscape files with no avail as to where I'm supposed to find that stupid "administration" file. So I'm beyond confused right now, and too tired to care about having too much pride to ask for help.
So here I am asking for help, heck I don't even know if I posted this in the right place :/ I'm really sorry if I didn't, I'm new but a quick learner and ready and willing to learn. So help me out here and I'll be extremely grateful![br][size=1]Posted at: November 06, 2006, 01:45:30 AM[/size][hr]Alright someone please help me. I'm beginning to think its my router but the tuts I've read have not helped me at ALL with my router.[br][size=1]Posted at: November 06, 2006, 12:41:59 PM[/size][hr]I know ya'll can help me with this.
